data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! Due to the current economic situation, builder has slashed prices on these new homes in NE Grand Junction, CO by JCI Construction, so they are more affordable for YOU!  Three bedroom two bathroom home. These are quality homes with a great style, in a fantastic location close to schools, shopping, ice cream, and the potential 29 Road and I 70 interchange. Custom built ranch-style home with upgraded cabinetry, laminate flooring, ceramic tile in front entry, covered patio, and two car garage. Designer kitchen includes pantry, dishwasher, a gas stove/oven, and micro-hood. We can add landscaping and fencing to your home, as well as decorative metal siding if you so choose! We have 52 lots and eight floor plans to choose from. Call listing agent for details.
